Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's so hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fry to death...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.03,0:00:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta eat this before it melts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:25.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there is no summer without this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.31,0:00:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Blackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.13,0:01:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shift change.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.54,0:01:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.46,0:01:06.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He hasn't moved from there lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.51,0:01:10.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I give him food he doesn't even look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He's smart so he might have realized it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:23.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happens to familiars when they learn that their master has died?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.56,0:01:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ssh, what if he heard?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I thought he wouldn't hear from this distance.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably he'll revert to a demon with the connection gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.56,0:01:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wouldn't be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:31.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.44,0:03:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They were sold out at the shop so I had to go all the way to the one behind the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.77,0:03:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it's so hellishly hot in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.58,0:03:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fancy school like this really should at least have aircon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.29,0:03:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it, this is an old building.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.38,0:03:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we didn't have aircon where we grew up, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fan should be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.00,0:03:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, did you buy the mineral water I asked you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... sorry, I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.50,0:04:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You see, the shadow of water is too pale... since it's transparent.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.01,0:04:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, want my ice cream?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.95,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bought two for yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.83,0:04:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No thanks, I'll go buy some myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.18,0:04:19.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.08,0:04:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, why do I have to do homework and reports on a sunday like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I became that Esquire something, but nothing's changed from being a Page.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And look at this, Esquire is still at the bottom of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you on this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.60,0:04:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Middle First Class.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not so high either!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're one to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long would it take to become the top, a Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really want to go on missions and get some practical experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:21.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paladin is a title given to only one person at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.86,0:05:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not a rank that anyone can get.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you won't be going on missions for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.77,0:05:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.57,0:05:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You often ignore orders and act on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:36.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still can't run errands at your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.84,0:05:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No surprise there, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the problem, I said I was sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:41.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.71,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You depend too much on Satan's power when you fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.27,0:05:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should stop drawing your sword all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you shouldn't use your body as a shield just because you heal quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.82,0:06:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep on like this you'll get possessed by Satan's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it matter, I helped you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't preach like the old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were about to go down!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.25,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you this for your own sake! Father would do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.81,0:06:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's probably rolling in his grave worrying about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.74,0:06:25.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if the shitty old geezer was such a worrywart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.04,0:06:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shitty old geezer? How long are you going to act like a rebellious child?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you grow up already?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.30,0:06:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And how long are you going to act all cool and adult?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.13,0:06:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get so full of yourself just because Shiemi always stares at you like you're the Eighth Wonder!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.01,0:06:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does Shiemi have to do with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not staring at me at all, and I'm not full of myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.21,0:06:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of couse she is! You're wearing glasses but you don't even notice that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.51,0:06:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one stupid four-eyes for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:07:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid? Says my brother who can't even run errands at his age?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still going on about that? Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.50,0:07:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your fighting is the same. You rely on power because you have neither knowledge nor skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.21,0:07:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Use your head a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.97,0:07:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A miracle! A miracle just happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.51,0:07:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing to laugh about!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Okumura here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.36,0:07:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood. I'm coming right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.50,0:07:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.19,0:07:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many spares does he have?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.32,0:08:08.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Yukio Okumura, Middle First Class Exorcist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Rin Okumura, Esquire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.21,0:08:15.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin! What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.58,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about your glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not even making sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't have time to play with you now! Go home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.85,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.31,0:08:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.79,0:08:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explain the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.82,0:08:32.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blackie, the guardian Cat Sith of the southern rear gate has gone berserk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.66,0:08:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have sealed a mile of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.32,0:08:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.74,0:08:49.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.51,0:08:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right? What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.84,0:08:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly he got all big and attacked us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.54,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I let it slip that Reverend Fujimoto is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.26,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He probably heard us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.96,0:09:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry. What's going to happen to Blackie now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.77,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be all right. We Exorcists will sort it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.36,0:09:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sort it out? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on? What does this have to do with the geezer's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Cat Sith was Father's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The geezer's? What's a Cat Sith?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.62,0:09:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are demons that look like cats.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.02,0:09:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Japanese ones' tail splits if they live long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.69,0:09:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Cat Sith was a protective god of silk for hundreds of years, and people worshipped him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He protected silk from mice and fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.35,0:09:50.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, the people celebrated him and they lived in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.69,0:10:03.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as they stopped manufacturing silk, he was forgotten as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.38,0:10:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.11,0:10:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having lost his place, he became a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.44,0:10:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! It's not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.48,0:10:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{halftime}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okumura!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0027,,{\q2}Holy water, holy silver, holy wine\N\Nand holy medicines don't work either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.52,0:11:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0020,,And we don't know his fatal verse yet, so Aria can't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.64,0:11:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0027,,{\q2}We hit him with lots of tranquilizers so\N\Nhe's slowed down a bit, but he recovers fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.11,0:11:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Reverend Fujimoto tell you anything about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.67,0:11:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were there on that mission, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.00,0:11:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.50,0:11:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukio was still an Esquire back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.18,0:12:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a construction site in a certain village, more and more accidents happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.08,0:12:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The locals feared that something was haunting it, so they called worshippers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.09,0:12:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter what they did it didn't help much, and the situation got hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.19,0:12:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As their last reserve, they called the True Cross Knight Order.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Paladin Fujimoto was appointed to kill the demonic god.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.79,0:12:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I'll be fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.66,0:13:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really impressing how he calmed the situation without spilling a drop of blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.57,0:13:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old geezer was a Paladin?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.88,0:13:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it started...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.13,0:13:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Father named him Blackie and made a familiar contract with him to guard the gate of the Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.31,0:13:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's a demon after all. He lost his master and returned to his true nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father prepared this just in case a situation like this would come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If something happens to me and you can't cope with Blackie, use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.84,0:13:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made this myself, it'll calm him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a reworked grenade, so it will probably kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.55,0:13:47.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.15,0:13:53.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we don't know what kind of grenade it is or how powerful it is, so I'll do it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.64,0:14:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liars! Shiro is the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.59,0:14:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Need assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only need to throw it at him so I'm fine by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.59,0:14:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's prepare for the worst and evacuate all other personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.71,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, fall back to the gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.99,0:14:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro can't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.72,0:14:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro will be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He will be back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.52,0:14:30.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.42,0:14:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin, you should retreat as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This drug might work on you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.11,0:14:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to kill him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.36,0:14:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. There's no Exorcist at the Academy who could tame a demon of this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.07,0:14:50.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we have no choice but to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.87,0:14:53.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro will come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.17,0:14:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't die until then either!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.67,0:15:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retreat already, Rin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.28,0:15:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.05,0:15:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's just sad. You shouldn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.12,0:15:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.91,0:15:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.29,0:15:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Telepathy between demons, I guess?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.82,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even then, we can't leave him like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then before that, let me try convince him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.46,0:15:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Convince?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.78,0:15:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I won't draw my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.35,0:15:35.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight using my head and without relying on Satan, just as you told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.33,0:15:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.09,0:15:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.36,0:15:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.34,0:15:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Rin Okumura! Shiro's son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.69,0:15:59.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro's?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.94,0:16:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.46,0:16:06.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! I don't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.16,0:16:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar! Don't lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.39,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really used his head...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.14,0:16:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You loved my dad a lot, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.09,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got so sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:17:01.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the same. Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.16,0:17:09.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rin...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.96,0:17:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You loved humans a lot, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.29,0:17:26.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you got so sad when they forgot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.61,0:17:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought you some catnip wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.24,0:17:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.66,0:18:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't meet anymore? Shiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.59,0:18:18.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really die?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.79,0:18:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.31,0:18:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't fight at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.89,0:19:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's always like this. It annoys the hell out of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.16,0:19:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you want to go serious on him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.87,0:19:13.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do. But before that I'd like to learn more about this Japan you love so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.31,0:19:22.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's lovely. But I didn't give you the infinity key for sightseeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will it be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.36,0:19:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looked interested enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:19:57.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for the wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:19:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.76,0:20:02.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's already attached to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.22,0:20:06.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going to happen to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to great lengths and made them let you take him as your familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.94,0:20:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some other familiar will become the guardian of the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.24,0:20:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's poison!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This smells like Shiro's present!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.65,0:20:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? He says it smells like Dad's present.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.36,0:20:39.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is catnip wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.42,0:20:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Catnip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.09,0:20:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro's catnip wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.48,0:20:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me! Give me wine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.67,0:20:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I should've known Father wouldn't hurt Blackie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.79,0:21:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't expect the old geezer was this amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.96,0:21:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So good!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.42,0:23:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's raise a toast to Blackie and the old geezer!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.02,0:23:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't, Rin. This isn't made for humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.47,0:23:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine, just a gesture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.50,0:23:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, as a memory!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.13,0:23:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drink it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.35,0:23:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.28,0:23:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.88,0:23:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.08,0:23:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.46,0:23:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shiro's catnip wine's so good...
