Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:37.98,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,doushitatte kanawanai esoragoto darou ga
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:42.48,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mune wo moyasu hi wa dare ni mo keseya shinai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:47.74,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,sora kara furu kuroi ame ga kono mi nurashi furitomanakutomo
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:53.16,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada ore wa kawareru jibun de kaetemiseru
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:58.63,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}kore ga sou "pride" sorezore no basho de
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:02.96,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,717)}mada mada kieru na kokoro no hi wo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:08.43,OPromaji,,0000,0000,0000,,mada mada ikeru zo ikeru zo
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.23,0:01:55.60,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,After birth, people live as they wish
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:58.23,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,They then learn the black box in their head; is that bliss?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.23,0:02:00.78,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Just cross over, beyond the line of your limit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, take a step, and I mean this minute
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.74,0:02:09.03,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Life's a bitch, so if it's easy, you're doing it wrong
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.03,0:02:14.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, which way is the world going? Then ignore it and go wherever (here we go)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.16,0:02:18.92,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,There are things I could never have, things with time
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.25,0:02:23.51,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there a reason I force my heart upon them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.01,0:02:29.02,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I never tried to understand, I just forced it on them
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.26,0:02:32.89,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm no better than those lifeless adults
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.89,0:02:37.98,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a pipe dream I could never have
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:42.48,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But no one can put out the fire in my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:47.74,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,The black rain may pour hard and leave me drenched
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.74,0:02:53.16,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,But I know I can change, I will change myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.58,0:02:58.63,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}This is my pride, what makes up my core
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.13,0:03:02.96,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,0)\pos(640,15)}I won't let my fire be put out; not yet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.96,0:03:08.43,OP,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll keep going, and I'll never stop
